scene.message:
Nanjo: Code Breaker...{nl}
I used to play it with{nl}
Yamaoka long ago.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: The other day that guy{nl}
got caught playing Daihinmin{nl}
for money in class and got{nl}
scolded by the teacher.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Forget the gambling{nl}
fan, let's get to the{nl}
hospital — before I snap.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Gambling — a man's{nl}
dream! Casinos — bunny girls!{waitkey}Slots, blackjack,{nl}
Code Breaker... ahh, I wish{nl}
I were old enough to hit{nl}
the casino already.{waitkey}{ret}
